HEADWORD: Ruthless
<hw>Ruth"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having no ruth; cruel;
pitiless.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Their rage the hostile bands restrain,⟦br⟧
All but the <qex>ruthless</qex> monarch of the main.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Ruth"less*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Ruth"less*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

